</div><div class='PageContent'>
	<div class='LeftHandBlock'>
		<div class='Inner'><div class="ColumnSection">
Interviewed by Harry Kroto and video recorded in 2005.<br />&nbsp;<p align="center" />
 <div align="center">
    <p>


			<video id="video_player" class="video-js vjs-default-skin"
			  controls width="480" height="360"
			  poster="/images/video_preview.jpg"
			  data-setup='{"example_option":true}'>
